= TTF_SetFontDirection =

Set direction per font.

== Syntax ==

<syntaxhighlight lang='c'>
int TTF_SetFontDirection(TTF_Font *font, TTF_Direction direction);
</syntaxhighlight>

== Function Parameters ==

{|
|'''font'''
|[[TTF_Font]] handle
|-
|'''direction'''
|[[TTF_Direction]] parameter
|}

== Return Value ==

Returns 0, or -1 if SDL_ttf is not compiled with HarfBuzz or invalid
parameter

== Remarks ==

It overrides the global direction set with the deprecated
[[TTF_SetDirection]]().

